mystery.title: Mystery
mystery.description: The largest collections of who-done-its you'll find anywhere!

289781.title: After Life
289781.description: A woman is pronounced dead after a horrific car accident. The funeral director is preparing her body for the funeral when she wakes up.

292823.title: The New Daughter
292823.description: A single father moves to South Carolina with his two children and soon begins to notice his daughter exhibiting increasingly strange behavior.

299580.title: The Big Easy
299580.description: A new female district attorney is unhappy with the gangs and corruption in New Orleans and bonds with a detective in this sultry crime thriller.

299591.title: Suicide Kings
299591.description: A group of rich twenty-somethings kidnap a crime boss and use his money to pay a ransom for one of their sisters, who was also kidnapped.

300169.title: The Ninth Gate
300169.description: A rare-book dealer acquires a demonic manuscript, leading to a series of terrifying supernatural occurrences as he uncovers the truth about the book.

300463.title: Return of the Pink Panther
300463.description: Dispatched to a Swiss resort town, Clouseau must investigate cat-burglar Sir Charles and his wife Claudine through a series of hilarious disguises.

301153.title: Leviathan
301153.description: An underwater exploration team is trapped five miles beneath the ocean's surface with a creature that cannot die and exists only to kill.

301814.title: The Pink Panther 2
301814.description: Inspector Clouseau is back! This time, he's teaming up with a squad of international detectives to stop a globe-trotting thief from striking again.

301937.title: The Private Life of Sherlock Holmes
301937.description: Sherlock Holmes and Dr. Watson accept a strange investigation of a missing man that takes them to Scotland and the Loch Ness monster.

302360.title: Fire With Fire
302360.description: A fireman, in Witness Protection after seeing a white supremacist commit a brutal crime, decides to take action when he finds himself threatened.

302708.title: The Long Goodbye
302708.description: In this neo-noir thriller, a private detective is determined to solve a difficult case after he becomes a suspect in the murder of his friend’s wife.

302719.title: Mulholland Falls
302719.description: Set in the 1950s, a squad of crooked cops try to cover up the murder of a young woman when they realize just how deep her romantic ties go.

303078.title: Cotton Comes To Harlem
303078.description: Two Harlem cops investigate a robbery, believing that a reverend has staged it in order to steal the money he’s collected for a local fundraiser.

305015.title: Gorky Park
305015.description: In the Soviet Union, a Russian police officer is caught up in a twisted murder mystery when three bodies are discovered in Moscow’s Gorky Park.

305031.title: Witness For The Prosecution
305031.description: A courtroom drama about a young man on trial for a wealthy widow's murder after he suspiciously profits from her will.

306921.title: Breakheart Pass
306921.description: Charles Bronson stars in this nerve-shattering mystery thriller about a treacherous train ride across the snowy western frontier.  Also stars Richard Crenna and Jill Ireland.

308307.title: Buried
308307.description: Paul Conroy wakes up buried six feet underground with a lighter, a rapidly dying cell phone, low oxygen and no idea who put him there or why.

312191.title: Poltergeist II: The Other Side
312191.description: After moving to a new home, the ghastly ghosts return to battle the Freeling family once more for the soul of a young clairvoyant.

312411.title: Basic Instinct 2: Risk Addiction
312411.description: After breaking the law again, Catherine Tramell is evaluated by a psychologist at Scotland Yard who utimately finds her more and more irresistible.

313931.title: Stir of Echoes
313931.description: After being hypnotized, Tom (Kevin Bacon) is haunted by terrifying visions that seem to be sending him a message from beyond.

316455.title: Sorority Row
316455.description: Five sorority sisters take a prank too far, resulting in tragedy, but cover up the incident until it comes back to haunt them a year later.

321856.title: The Blair Witch Project
321856.description: A trio of filmmakers trek to uncover an urban legend, becomes an excursion into heart-stopping terror, in the original "found footage" horror.

326245.title: Dial M For Murder
326245.description: When an ex-tennis pro’s plan to murder his cheating wife and steal her inheritance goes awry, he must find a way to evade the law.

326924.title: Minor Details
326924.description: When the students at a wealthy boarding school start to become mysteriously ill, several teenagers work together to solve the case.

332936.title: Lake Mungo
332936.description: A family mourns the death of its 16-year-old daughter, Alice. Upon discovering her secret double life, a series of clues lead them to Lake Mungo.

348926.title: Abandoned
348926.description: When a woman drops off her new boyfriend at the hospital for minor outpatient surgery, she returns to find that he has inexplicably dissappeared.

358575.title: Mississippi Burning
358575.description: Based on the true story, two FBI agents investigate the disappearance of three Mississippi civil rights activists in 1964.

376074.title: My Husband's Double Life
376074.description: When her perfect husband kills himself, Elizabeth discovers his death may be more than suicide and starts to seek the truth.

404573.title: Dressed to Kill
404573.description: A psycho-killer stalks two women - a frustrated housewife and a street-smart hooker who teams up with the first woman's son to set a trap.

435625.title: The Hollow
435625.description: When a congressman’s daughter is murdered in a Mississippi town, FBI agents put their lives in peril as they uncover a far-reaching web of corruption.

464287.title: Forgiveness
464287.description: A beloved Pastor works to serve his 'flock' and save his church. In his dedication and desire to do so, he crosses uncrossable boundaries.

464288.title: Returned
464288.description: A missing man returns 12 years after his flight disappeared, searching for answers with the assistance of a beautiful and mysterious woman.

465163.title: The Boys From Brazil
465163.description: A Nazi-hunter chases infamous Dr. Josef Mengele, who has escaped to Paraguay to revive the Third Reich

465251.title: The Oxford Murders
465251.description: When an American student enrolls at Oxford, and his landlady is murdered, he and his professor try to foil a killer who leaves mathematical clues.

466705.title: Wild Horses
466705.description: When a detective re-opens a 15-year-old cold case, he suspects that a boy who went missing was murdered, and that a local rancher was involved.

466963.title: The Exorcist III
466963.description: A police lieutenant seeks answers in a psychiatric ward, when he ties a string of current murders to those of a serial killer executed long ago.

467574.title: Harvest Lake
467574.description: Five friends enter a mysterious forest where they fall under the spell of a lusty, otherworldly entity that threatens to alter their lives forever.

472908.title: Odd Thomas
472908.description: In a small desert town, a fry cook with psychic gifts, his girlfriend, and the sheriff team up to stop a weird stranger from unleashing an evil force.

475051.title: In the Electric Mist
475051.description: A seasoned detective untangles a web of corruption and murder as he descends into Cajun country and the dark, sultry world of a New Orleans mobster.

476219.title: Jack Goes Home
476219.description: After his father dies in a car crash, a man returns home to care for his injured mother and uncovers secrets that make him question his very identity.

480219.title: The Haunting of La Llorona
480219.description: La Llorona, a horrifying demon whose cries are nightmarish legend, victimizes an assault survivor and her best friend while challenging a priest.

488965.title: The Pink Panther
488965.description: In this remake, the bumbling Inspector Jacques Clouseau tries to solve the murder and theft of a famous soccer coach and his priceless diamond ring.

491715.title: Hell House LLC
491715.description: Five years after the deadly opening night of a Halloween attraction, a documentary film crew investigates the haunted house where it all took place.

493370.title: The Whole Truth
493370.description: A lawyer fights to clear a teen in the brutal stabbing of his father but, as more evidence comes to light, the whole truth is darker than he thought.

494843.title: The Lazarus Effect
494843.description: A group of medical researchers finds a way to revive the dead, but when their project is shut down, they continue anyway, with horrific consequences.

495392.title: Freshman Fall
495392.description: A timid college freshman drugged and sexually assaulted at a fraternity party fights to prosecute her rapist in the absence of evidence.

497888.title: Across the Hall
497888.description: Convinced that his fiancée is cheating on him, a man follows her to a seedy hotel, where his best friend comes to his aid to try to avert disaster.

499222.title: Tales From the Crypt
499222.description: After five strangers get hopelessly lost in a crypt, they meet its mysterious Keeper, who describes to them how they will each die.

499338.title: Population Zero
499338.description: In 2009, three young men were killed in a remote part of Yellowstone National Park. The only thing more shocking are the bizarre events that followed.

505984.title: Last Shift
505984.description: A rookie cop oversees the last shift at a closing police station, but soon discovers the building’s connection to a cult, and all hell breaks loose.

506051.title: A Wife's Nightmare
506051.description: A woman recovering from a mental breakdown is forced to welcome and open her home to an enigmatic stranger, who claims to be her husband’s daughter.

506052.title: A Daughter's Nightmare
506052.description: After her father dies, a young woman begins to suspect that the mysterious man her mother met in a support group might have sinister intentions.

506145.title: The Wailing
506145.description: A policeman races against time to save his daughter from a mysterious sickness spreading through a small village.

506532.title: Sins of the Preacher
506532.description: A mother is out for justice when she realizes her daughter's alleged suicide may have actually been murder at the hands of her minister husband.

507477.title: The Ghost Writer
507477.description: A writer agrees to author the memoirs of a former Prime Minister only to learn that he is a war criminal and that his first writer was found dead.

512098.title: The Columbine Massacre: In the Killer's Mind
512098.description: In 1999, two students arrived at Colorado High School armed to the teeth, executed 13 people and wounded dozens of others before committing suicide.

513104.title: Solver
513104.description: Arriving at his late grandfather’s cabin, a young professional discovers a series of puzzles that lead him and his friends to a dangerous secret.

515413.title: All Good Things
515413.description: A perfect love story, or the perfect crime? The truth emerges about a 1980s NY real estate heir, suspected, but never tried for murdering his wife

521583.title: Triple Dog
521583.description: A slumber party of six high school girls turns into a game of dares that spirals out of control and leaves their lives changed in devastating ways.

532534.title: Sherlock Holmes Y El Arma Secreta
532534.description: Un científico suizo ha creado un arma que cambiaría el curso de la Segunda Guerra Mundial y Sherlock Holmes se ocupará de que no caiga en manos nazis.

533526.title: Sherlock Holmes: La Mujer De Verde
533526.description: Las víctimas de una serie de asesinatos tienen en común un dedo cortado. Holmes sospecha de Moriarty, pero las pistas apuntan a una misteriosa mujer.

533563.title: Sherlock Holmes: Terror en La Noche
533563.description: A Holmes lo contratan para evitar el robo de un enorme diamante durante un viaje en tren. En el trayecto, hay un asesinato y la piedra desaparece.

546980.title: Clive Barker's Lord of Illusions
546980.description: While on assignment in LA, a New York private eye stumbles into a case full of supernatural intrigue when a cult leader and illusionist is murdered.

559765.title: The Hound of the Baskervilles
559765.description: Sherlock Holmes and Dr. Watson investigate the legend of a supernatural hound who may be stalking a young heir on his fog-shrouded estate.

570419.title: D.O.A. Con Las Horas Contadas (Doblado)
570419.description: A Frank Bigelow le acaban de decir  que ha sido envenenado y que solo le quedan unos dias de vida, ahora tiene de averiguar quien lo mato y por que.

587303.title: Lying Eyes
587303.description: A popular high school cheerleader is romanced by a rich older man. When she learns he’s married and tries to leave him, he vows to kill her.

592462.title: Where She Lies
592462.description: An assaulted American teen in the early 1960s gives birth and is told her baby died until decades later a deathbed confession changes that reality.

602959.title: La Muerte Sonrie Al Asesino (Doblado)
602959.description: Una mujer misteriosa con amnesia entra en un triángulo amoroso mortal con la pareja que la acoge y su espantoso pasado se va revelando.

607423.title: High Lonesome
607423.description: In Big Bend Country in Texas, a recent spate of unsolved murders get pinned on a mysterious young drifter in town who gets caught up with bad actors.

609164.title: Distorted
609164.description: After moving into an ultra-secure building, a woman suspects something sinister about the surveillance and technology that surrounds her.

615210.title: Bordertown
615210.description: A tenacious reporter investigates the murders of young women in a town on the border that divides Texas from Mexico.

615211.title: The Pledge
615211.description: A recently retired detective cannot get over an unsolved murder case, so he abandons his personal plans and devotes his new life to finding justice.

615655.title: Masacre en El Autocine (Doblado)
615655.description: Dos detectives intentan atrapar a un asesino en serie que acecha un autocine en una zona rural de California y mata a personas al azar con una espada.

616099.title: Caught
616099.description: Inspired by a true story, a desperate housewife kidnaps her husband's teenage mistress as a prank, but her plans soon spiral out of control.

618217.title: Contract Killers
618217.description: A fierce assassin for the CIA has to untangle and expose a rogue government conspiracy to destroy the U.S. economy before they kill her to be silent.

621683.title: Ace Ventura: Pet Detective
621683.description: When the mascot for football’s Miami Dolphins is stolen, a wacky detective goes undercover, underwater, and in over his head, to get his man or beast.

622108.title: El Murcielago (Doblado)
622108.description: Una escritora de novelas de misterio alquila una mansión que no hace mucho fue el escenario de los violentos crímenes de un tal Murciélago.

622708.title: 10 Year Reunion
622708.description: During a high school reunion, the four members of an inseparable clique unearth a time capsule and learn the death of their friend wasn’t an accident.

625337.title: La Desaparición del Vuelo 412 (Doblado)
625337.description: El vuelo 412 es testigo de la desaparición de dos aviones de combate que van a interceptar un OVNI, pero la Fuerza Aérea decide encubrir el incidente.

625338.title: The Disappearance of Flight 412
625338.description: A flight crew executing a test mission witnesses the disappearance of two fighter-jets out to intercept a UFO, but the Air Force devises a cover-up.

627912.title: Paintsville: The April Pennington Story
627912.description: This doc follows the 1991 mysterious death of 16-year-old April Renee Pennington.

641063.title: An Unknown Compelling Force
641063.description: This documentary investigates the 1959 case of nine Russian hikers who died under mysterious circumstances, fueling conspiracy theories.

642415.title: Suburban Nightmare: Chris Watts
642415.description: Chris Watts appeared to have a perfect life until he shockingly confesses to strangling his pregnant wife and two daughters.

649963.title: Freaks
649963.description: A little girl who has been shut away from the outside world by her father soon discovers a dangerous universe awaiting beyond her front door.

650014.title: The Crickets Dance
650014.description: A woman who inherits an antebellum Southern home finds a journal and makes a life-changing journey when she looks for the diary's owner.

651461.title: A Mother's Rage
651461.description: Lori Laughlin stars as a mother driving her daughter to her new college who ferociously fights off a psychotic person terrorizing them on the highway.

652136.title: Zoe Gone
652136.description: After a sixteen-year-old’s daughter goes missing, it’s up to the teen mom to step up and find her baby after others in her life fail to do so.

654968.title: Out of Control
654968.description: Against her father's wishes a young Chicago cop pursues her dream of becoming a detective when she's brought on to investigate a major murder case.

659502.title: Deadly Cheer Mom
659502.description: When the cheer captain gets kicked off the team for salacious but fake party videos, she sets out to catch the saboteur and prove her innocence.

659580.title: Arabella Black Angel
659580.description: An insatiable sex addict and her writer husband hatch a scheme that lures and then murders her lovers for use as material for his upcoming book.

660332.title: Ann Rule's Everything She Ever Wanted
660332.description: A sensual, self-assured Southern belle uses her easily influenced husband, and any other means necessary, to ascend the ranks of Atlanta's elite.

660520.title: Extraordinary: The Revelations
660520.description: An exploration of ET history, UFO belief paradigms, and testimony from military whistleblowers tackles age-old questions about possible alien agendas.

661435.title: The Surprise Visit
661435.description: In this thriller based on a true story, two young drug addicts' botched robbery leads to a nightmarish situation for both them and the victims.

662955.title: Secret in Their Eyes
662955.description: A team of detectives is torn apart when one of their children is brutally murdered. The ensuing 13-year investigation ends with a shocking secret.

663315.title: Appointment with Death
663315.description: Who planned the demise of Mrs. Boynton? Only the gifted sleuth Hercule has the skills to solve this murder! Based on the novel by Agatha Christie.

671334.title: Most Shocking Celebrity Deaths of All Time
671334.description: With the world at your feet, life in the spotlight is the stuff of dreams. But dreams can turn to nightmares faster than anyone can imagine.

672228.title: The Recall
672228.description: When five friends vacation at a remote lake house, they are unaware that planet Earth is under an alien invasion and mass-abduction.

672503.title: Death on the Nile
672503.description: While detective Hercule Poirot is enjoying some R&R on a luxurious cruise down the Nile River, a newlywed heiress is found murdered on board.

672505.title: Sins of the Father: The Green River Killer
672505.description: Tap into the mind of the ‘Green River Killer’ as his son looks back on his relationship with his father, who killed at least 50 women while masquerading as a normal suburban dad.

673330.title: The Forbidden Empire
673330.description: An 18th century cartographer discovers hidden dark secrets and dangerous creatures after setting out to map the uncharted lands of Transylvania.

675565.title: Aliens, Abductions, and UFOs: Roswell at 75
675565.description: Explore why Americans became obsessed with proving alien existence through eyewitness interviews, abductees, and scientific experts – all to make you believe: we are not alone.

676663.title: The Clovehitch Killer
676663.description: A picture-perfect family is shattered when the work of a serial killer, with a body count of at least ten women, hits too close to home.

678067.title: Killing Diana
678067.description: On the 25th anniversary of her death, we dive into the mystery surrounding Princess Diana’s fatal car crash.

678947.title: Dear Frank
678947.description: After Frank's wife is mysteriously poisoned, he finds a diary indicating the identities of her previous lovers, who may be suspects in her murder.

680248.title: Spinning Man
680248.description: When a female student goes missing, a popular professor is the prime suspect. Suddenly, the questions he faces become a matter of life or death.

680696.title: The Ravine
680696.description: A family is torn apart after a loving father and husband commits a series of heinous crimes and the reasoning behind it has gone to the grave with the accused.

681622.title: Parkland
681622.description: A recounting of the chaotic events that occurred at Dallas' Parkland Hospital on the day U.S. President John F. Kennedy was assassinated.

682049.title: Charada "La Farsa" (Doblado)
682049.description: Romance y suspenso en París. Una viuda es perseguida por varios hombres que quieren la fortuna que le había robado su marido asesinado.

682349.title: Arctic Void
682349.description: All but three men vanish from a tourist ship in the Arctic and fear becomes the master when a dark truth emerges that compels them to ally or perish.

682615.title: The Bourne Ultimatum
682615.description: Jason Bourne flees a new generation of skilled CIA operatives in a non-stop race around the globe while seeking the truth behind his mysterious past.

682628.title: The Bourne Legacy
682628.description: Agent Aaron Cross uses his genetically enhanced skills to evade the CIA after Jason Bourne's actions lead to the termination of his black ops program.

684143.title: Devil's Pass
684143.description: In this intense thriller, five young adventurers retrace the steps of a doomed group of hikers in pursuit of a legendary paranormal mystery.

684168.title: Return to Sender
684168.description: A perfectionist nurse has her world shattered after a blind date results in a brutal assault. But she won't let her attacker get the last word.

685543.title: Ear 2 Ear
685543.description: This film is about a family suffering from mental illness who discovers each other's condition while trying to get justice for their brother's death.

688864.title: Death Clique
688864.description: Inspired by true events, a jealous rivalry between two inseparable friends and the new girl at school leads to a shocking and violent crime.

689652.title: In the Heat of the Night
689652.description: While traveling in the deep south, a black Philadelphian homicide detective becomes embroiled in a murder investigation.

690644.title: Playdate
690644.description: After befriending her new neighbors, a woman suspects their hiding of a deadly secret after her daughter is injured during a playdate with their son.

691877.title: The Raven
691877.description: A young Baltimore detective joins forces with Edgar Allan Poe to stop a madman from  committing horrific murders inspired by the writer’s own works.

692691.title: Somebody Help Me
692691.description: A trip to Lake Arrowhead for a birthday celebration turns into a tangled web of terror when, one by one, members of the party begin disappearing,

693659.title: Archive
693659.description: 2038. A roboticist has been working on a human-equivalent android, with each prototype being an increasingly advanced version of his deceased wife.

697439.title: Somebody Help Me 2
697439.description: Approaching the anniversary of the events at the cabin, Brendan’s worst fears come to life one night when his wife and niece don't return home.

701202.title: Damascus Cover
701202.description: After a mission to smuggle a chemical weapons scientist out of Syria goes wrong, a spy discovers he is a pawn in a much bigger plan.

702047.title: The Livingston Gardener
702047.description: A serial killer on death row reveals in one final interview that his victims are still alive. Can the detective beat him at his diabolical game?

702672.title: Vacaciones De Terror
702672.description: Una familia adinerada hereda una casa vacacional que se encuentra embrujada por el espíritu de una bruja que fue quemada en la hoguera.

705017.title: Immortal City Records
705017.description: A struggling singer’s dream job with hip-hop legends becomes a nightmare when she suspects her bosses are murderers.

707381.title: Girls Getaway Gone Wrong 2
707381.description: When three best friends reunite for a girls’ trip to Fashion Week, they become the prime suspects when a designer goes missing.

709363.title: Moorehouse Road
709363.description: While road tripping in search of a new life, two newlyweds and their friend take a detour to a mysterious hotel and check-in to a nightmare.

710116.title: Deus: The Dark Sphere
710116.description: Sent to investigate a mysterious black sphere orbiting Mars, astronauts wake from 8 months of hibernation to discover a strange transmission.

711155.title: Shut In
711155.description: A widowed child psychologist living a rural, isolated existence becomes convinced the ghost of a missing boy is haunting her and her bedridden son.

711204.title: In the Heat of the Night: A Matter of Justice
711204.description: When a serial killer of women is on the loose in Sparta, all the clues lead Sheriff Gillespie and Forbes to the home of the wealthy Judge Walker.

711205.title: In the Heat of the Night: By Duty Bound
711205.description: Political intrigue arrives in remote Sparta when Gillespie's enemies find a local businessman to run against him in his next bid for county sheriff.

711206.title: In the Heat of the Night: Who Was Geli Bendl?
711206.description: All eyes are on Sparta after an internationally renowned actress arrives unexpectedly in the rural Mississippi town—and with a killer secret.

711708.title: The Hole in the Ground
711708.description: A woman suspects that her son, who returned home after disappearing in the woods, is an imposter.

712641.title: The Last Letter
712641.description: A young woman grapples with a debilitating sleep disorder as her husband struggles to cope after the birth of their son.

713808.title: El Gato De Las Nueve Colas (Doblado)
713808.description: Un reportero intenta resolver una serie de asesinatos relacionados con los proyectos experimentales de investigación de una empresa farmacéutica.

713922.title: The Man in 3B
713922.description: A charismatic new tenant quickly makes his mark on a Queens apartment building, but his popularity soon results in a murder with many suspects.

714662.title: Hearts in Atlantis
714662.description: Bobby Garfield returns home for a boyhood friend’s funeral and recalls the magical summer of 1960 when a man with strange powers changed his world.

722685.title: TMZ Investigates: Lisa Marie Presley: Unending Tragedy
722685.description: New details about Lisa Marie Presley's unforeseen passing are revealed.

723249.title: What Lies Below
723249.description: Liberty returns from camp to an introduction by her mother’s fiancé, whose charm and beauty paint the picture of a man too perfect to be human.

723828.title: The Best Offer
723828.description: An eccentric and lonely art auctioneer becomes obsessed with a reclusive heiress he can’t see and who’s hired him to value her family’s collection.

724353.title: Girl on the Third Floor
724353.description: Don Koch tries to renovate a rundown house with a sordid history for his growing family, only to learn his new abode has other plans for them.

725990.title: The Limehouse Golem
725990.description: With the Limehouse Golem serial killer on the loose, Inspector Kildare must rely on help from a troubled witness to bring the maniac to justice.

726077.title: The Book of Revelation
726077.description: A professional dancer struggles to get over his trauma after being abducted and subjected to sexual and psychological torment by three hooded women.

726443.title: The Den
726443.description: A woman witnesses a brutal murder in an online chat and is immersed in a nightmare in which she and her loved ones are targeted for a similar fate.

100000216.title: Oldboy
100000216.description: An advertising executive finds himself kidnapped and held hostage for 20 years in solitary confinement without any indication of his captor's motive.

100000228.title: Wrecked
100000228.description: In this gripping thriller, a man trapped in a car wreck at the bottom of a cliff has no idea of how he got there and no way to escape.

100000249.title: Red Joan
100000249.description: A suburban British widow recounts her double life as a Soviet spy in this dramatic tale of passion, courage, and betrayal based on a true story.

100000267.title: Stolen
100000267.description: When a child's decades-old remains are unearthed, a detective becomes obsessed with a possible link between the case and his own son's disappearance.

100000270.title: Official Secrets
100000270.description: Featuring a world-class ensemble cast, this gripping true-life thriller follows a spy gone rogue, who risks everything to stop an unjust war.

100000434.title: Who's the Man?
100000434.description: In this hip-hop whodunnit, Doctor Dré and Ed Lover play two barbers-turned-policemen who find themselves investigating their friend’s murder.

100000585.title: Gone Before Her Time: Brittany Murphy
100000585.description: Scene-stealing starlet Brittany Murphy was destined for Hollywood’s A-list until her untimely and mysterious death turned out the lights on her lifelong dreams.

100000844.title: Exam
100000844.description: When eight candidates enter a windowless room to compete for a job at a mysterious and powerful company, the stakes soon become life or death.

100001012.title: County Line: All In
100001012.description: The murder of a crooked attorney on the county line forces two neighboring sheriffs to put aside their differences to take down the killer.

100001193.title: Out of Blue
100001193.description: A New Orleans detective hunts for the killer of a renowned astrophysicist and finds herself drawn into a mystery of cosmic proportions.

100001513.title: Meeting at Midnight
100001513.description: After a murder occurs during a séance, Charlie Chan must search for the killer amidst the numerous ghosts conjured up by a motley crew of mediums.

100001598.title: The Conjuring: The Devil Made Me Do It
100001598.description: Paranormal investigators Ed and Lorraine Warren uncover an occult conspiracy as they help a defendant argue that a demon forced him to commit murder.

100001601.title: Reminiscence
100001601.description: Nick Bannister, a private investigator of the mind, navigates the darkly alluring world of the past by helping his clients access lost memories.

100001721.title: Angel of Mine
100001721.description: In this intense thriller, a woman grieving over her daughter's death comes to believe the young daughter of a neighbor is her own.

100001815.title: Horror in the High Desert 2: Minerva
100001815.description: A recounting of the events that took place in 2018, when a string of tragedies unfolded in the high desert of North Eastern Nevada.

100001824.title: Sin Rastro (Doblado)

100001845.title: Dark Web: Descent Into Hell

100002054.title: Look Again
100002054.description: After a young woman's boyfriend is murdered by an intruder, things worsen when she meets her friend's new boyfriend and suspects him to be the killer.

100002544.title: The Perfect Student
100002544.description: A well-respected criminology professor becomes a target herself when she tries to establish the innocence of her star student in a murder case.

0300004985.title: Midsomer Murders

0300010237.title: Mrs. Columbo

0300006625.title: Charlie's Angels
0300006625.description: Three smart, stunning women use their lethal feminine charms and combat skills as PIs, assigned to crack cases via speakerphone by a mysterious boss.

0300008637.title: Mike Tyson Mysteries

04844.title: The New Scooby-Doo Mysteries

03971.title: The Mary Higgins Clark Collection

03046.title: Unsolved Mysteries With Robert Stack
